    <title>【攻略】世界灭亡共有幻想MAMIYA</title>
    <url>/posts/1.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><a target="_blank" href="http://kenkou-land.com/mamiya/"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/08/06/MAMIYA.webp" title="点击跳转至游戏官网"></a></p>
<h2 id="◈-故事梗概-STORYLINE"><a href="#◈-故事梗概-STORYLINE" class="headerlink" title="◈ 故事梗概 &#x2F; STORYLINE"></a><p style="font-size:30px">◈ 故事梗概 &#x2F; STORYLINE</p></h2><p>世界滅亡が予言された年、東京<br>Tokyo, during the year in which the world was prophesied to end.<br><br>空想と心中する勇気もなく<br>As we clung to reality,<br>現実にしがみついている僕たちは<br>too spineless to throw our lives away together,<br>マミヤと　出会う<br>we met Mamiya.<br><br>友人の葬式　弔う人々<br>At a friend’s funeral, the entire crowd was weeping and mourning,<br>しかし　人がひとり死んだところで世界は変わらず<br>while we thought to ourselves that the death of a single person had no meaningful impact on the world at large.<br>目が覚めれば　同じ日々の反芻<br>We slept, woke up, and went through the same daily grind as ever.<br>――そう　思っていた<br>At least, that’s how it was supposed to be.<br><br>マミヤが　現れるまでは<br>Then Mamiya appeared…<br><br>目の前に現れた“マミヤ”と名乗る謎の子ども<br>Before we even knew it, the mysterious child named Mamiya had wormed their way into our daily lives.<br>次第にそれは日常を侵食し　僕たちの拠り所となっていく<br>They slowly, but surely, became something of an emotional support. They’d brought us down a new path.<br><br>その先に　死が待っていようとも<br>A path that would surely lead us to our deaths…<br><br></p>
<h2 id="◈-世界滅亡共有幻想「マミヤ」-FallDown"><a href="#◈-世界滅亡共有幻想「マミヤ」-FallDown" class="headerlink" title="◈ 世界滅亡共有幻想「マミヤ」-FallDown-"></a><p style="font-size:30px">◈ 世界滅亡共有幻想「マミヤ」-FallDown-</p></h2><p style="font-size:25px">A Shared Illusion of the World’s End "MAMIYA" -FallDown-</p>

